diff:1251799706:1251799685:=26c26%0a%3c * /domains/%3cdomain>/.qmail-spam%0a---%0a> # /domains/%3cdomain>/.qmail-spam%0a28c28%0a%3c *./domains/%3cdomain>/.qmail-innocent (untested, as I've not seen any false positives yet)%0a---%0a> #./domains/%3cdomain>/.qmail-innocent (untested, as I've not seen any false positives yet)%0a30c30%0a%3c * By modifying the .qmail-default configuration file:%0a---%0a> # By modifying the .qmail-default configuration file:%0a
